; Hand-written fixture for the PDO-to-signal projection (CanTools.Net).
; TPDO1 carries the bit layout of python-canopen's test_pdo_map_bit_mapping;
; TPDO2 exercises dummy padding, a record member and a missing target;
; TPDO3 is disabled via COB-ID bit 31.

